text:
Bought their Yam Cake and brought home to pan fry.  it’s really good

Update : bought the carrot cake, didn’t taste ok was sour
Xiao nan yang staffs at bendemeer food court was super friendly. Highly recommend to everyone
Order a KL Hokkien Mee & Carrot Cake, taste is ok but both very salty. Never finish all.

Bought 1 Pkt of sticky rice dumpling (3 pcs) pork/mushroom/salted egg $13.50 from Parkway Parade Fairprice "Just Nanyang" stall on 19/5 noon. I told her I wanted with salted egg, which is $13.50, but I realised she gave me without salted egg on next day. I was angry with her dishonest.
